channel.title: Unfound - Rise [EP]
channel.description:
Heyo!
I'm releasing my EP "Rise" this Friday (the 1st) on SoundCloud, but am releasing it early to you guys because of all your great support! All sounds you hear are from Auxy and were mastered in FL12. Feel free to ask me questions if you're curious!
https://soundcloud.com/unfound/sets/rise/s-zzyCN
Thanks so much, Unfound
